item.title: Whistleblower: Feds helping evacuees lacked virus protection
item.description: WASHINGTON (AP) — A authorities whistleblower has filed a complaint alleging that some federal workers did now not contain the mandatory holding instruments or coaching when they were deployed to back Americans evacuated from China one day of the coronavirus outbreak.
